      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHALK AND CHEESE (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (22.58) in a Grade 5 at Shepparton. Can discover winning form. DR. ZAIDEN (6) was prominent throughout but too strong in the run home to score by 2.75 lengths (20.10) at Traralgon in Mix 6/7. Has failed to finish in the placings from two starts here. Can make it two on the bounce. NOSEY BLUEY (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (29.86) at Sandown behind Illuminator in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Winning chance. SOMERTON MICK (7) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.",
